# Salesforce Package
Install OEP Salesforce managed package "OEI Package":
Login to your organizations Salesforce instance. (If you do not already have an instance, go to Salesforce.com to learn more about Salesforce and its licensing options.)

Navigate to the app by entering the URL below depending on if the instance is a Sandbox or Production site:
Sandbox: https://test.salesforce.com/packaging/installPackage.apexp?p0=04t1N000000Gmmp
Production: https://login.salesforce.com/packaging/installPackage.apexp?p0=04t1N000000Gmmp

Enter the password: xxx 
Select “Install for all Users”
Accept conditions
Select Install

Go to Setup, search for Installed Packages, confirm “OEI Platform” is installed. Select OEI app to view and use it.

Reference the OEP Data Model for Object Relationships and Field level details for the Objects.  

